title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 18 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 18 2022
description:
New York Sun Publisher Dovid Efune joins Buck to talk free speech, taking on the New York Times. Andrew Cuomo on the comeback trail. Pelosi vs Rand Paul on gas prices. John Ondrasik of Five for Fighting tells us about his new viral Ukraine song about President Zelensky. Pelosi on Ukraine. C&B talk with Trump impersonator Captain Deplorable. Mailbag Friday: 24/7 VIP backs Buck on his first-ever March Madness brackets.
